17:52.863 --> 17:54.364
Practice was nuts yesterday.

17:55.783 --> 17:57.868
Now I've got nerves on top of it.

17:58.452 --> 18:00.329
- Tonight's the Liberty game?
- Yeah.

18:01.747 --> 18:03.999
You know, I can help with all that.
The muscles,

18:04.083 --> 18:05.876
- the nerves.
- No, that's okay, Mom.

18:06.460 --> 18:08.378
