at City Gym.

21:27.953 --> 21:28.953
Want something to drink?

21:31.290 --> 21:33.010
All right.
Sheriff will be here in a minute.

21:36.378 --> 21:39.256
[Ani] <i>Clay's arrest
and the assembly where it happened,</i>

21:40.090 --> 21:41.967
<i>it was about to change everything.</i>

21:42.759 --> 21:44.094
