22:57.626 --> 22:59.795
Yeah. You've heard stuff about me, right?

23:00.170 --> 23:02.714
Like I'm an asshole jock or whatever.

23:02.798 --> 23:05.300
I mean, I guess so, yeah.

23:06.885 --> 23:07.885
So?

23:12.808 --> 23:13.808
[door closing]

23:14.309 --> 23:15.769
[coach] So, what's up?

23:18.105 --> 23:19.564
