the way you led these guys,

23:31.827 --> 23:34.871
- it gives me hope for the future.
- That's the thing, Coach, is...

23:37.082 --> 23:38.083
I don't have a future.

23:40.502 --> 23:42.087
And I just need to accept that.

23:42.754 --> 23:44.339
Hey, don't quit on me. All right?

23:45.006 --> 23:47.134
Look, you still got a lot to offer.

23:47.217 --> 23:49.529
