I'm sure you'll learn to see that.

23:49.553 --> 23:50.595
I've made up my mind.

23:53.390 --> 23:54.433
Thank you, Coach.

23:56.017 --> 23:57.602
For everything. You've been...

24:03.733 --> 24:05.485
