24:16.496 --> 24:17.496
Well, uh...

24:19.207 --> 24:20.792
[Zach] Bye, I guess.

24:21.084 --> 24:23.086
Hey, you always got a home here,
Dempsey.

24:24.004 --> 24:25.589
Look, you can stop by anytime.

24:28.091 --> 24:29.301
No, I don't think I can.

24:40.061 --> 24:42.147
