if I wanted to.

25:07.088 --> 25:08.215
He's still back there.

25:09.508 --> 25:11.927
Probably gonna transfer him to County.

25:12.177 --> 25:13.177
Jesus!

25:16.681 --> 25:17.682
Are you okay?

25:18.808 --> 25:20.810
You would tell me if you weren't?

25:21.937 --> 25:24.064
'Cause clearly I don't always know.

25:35.909 --> 25:36.910
