25:39.412 --> 25:40.747
my mom had this boyfriend.

25:42.999 --> 25:45.627
This fucked-up guy
who would just get high with her.

25:48.672 --> 25:49.672
When...

25:50.298 --> 25:51.841
she'd pass out, he would...

25:54.886 --> 25:56.054
just come to my bed.

26:03.812 --> 26:05.146
At first, he would just...

26:07.524 --> 26:08.567
put his hands on me.

26:11.820 --> 26:12.821
Then he started...

26:15.365 --> 26:19.119
He started making me put my hands
on his...

26:22.747 --> 26:23.832
And he would be hard.

26:27.377 --> 26:28.377
He...

26:33.174 --> 26:34.174
He...

26:36.803 --> 26:38.513
[breathing shakily]

26:38.805 --> 26:41.516
He'd put his fingers in my mouth
and start to jerk off.

26:47.147 --> 26:49.316
He only lived with us
for a couple of years.

26:50.567 --> 26:51.568
