26:55.363 --> 26:56.781
When I was on the streets...

26:58.575 --> 26:59.701
and I needed money...

27:04.039 --> 27:05.040
I would do stuff...

27:06.666 --> 27:07.666
to guys.

27:09.919 --> 27:12.088
Sometimes, they would do stuff that...

27:14.424 --> 27:15.550
we didn't talk about.

27:18.178 --> 27:19.638
But that I didn't want to do.

27:24.225 --> 27:26.436
I just felt like I was five again, and...

27:27.687 --> 27:28.687
it was all my fault.

27:30.607 --> 27:31.607
Hey.

27:32.108 --> 27:33.318
I'm so sorry.

27:36.655 --> 27:37.655
