30:44.259 --> 30:46.427
Hey, all good. I got it.
I'll be right back.

30:55.019 --> 30:56.019
I'm sorry.

30:56.437 --> 30:58.317
I should've called,
but my mum went to bed early

30:58.398 --> 31:00.066
