31:45.153 --> 31:46.153
Clay, wait.

31:48.406 --> 31:49.407
[Ani] <i> I won't lie to you,</i>

31:50.450 --> 31:52.577
<i>at that moment, in his eyes</i>

31:53.036 --> 31:54.036
<i>I saw...</i>

31:54.662 --> 31:55.662
<i>anger.</i>

31:56.080 --> 31:58.082
<i>Hatred. But not for me.</i>

31:58.166 --> 31:59.500
[crowd cheering]

32:00.293 --> 32:01.293
[Ani] <i>For Bryce.</i>

32:01.836 --> 32:06.090
<i>Over the first half, the anger
and the hatred only burned hotter.</i>

32:06.341 --> 32:09.093
