he was ready to go after Bryce.</i>

32:09.260 --> 32:10.553
[air horn blaring]

32:12.430 --> 32:13.848
[chanting]

32:14.474 --> 32:16.059
[Ani] <i>He was about to get his chance.</i>

32:17.226 --> 32:20.688
