- I can't let Clay go to jail for this.

36:26.017 --> 36:28.311
- I have to go to the cops.
- Listen to me. Listen.

36:28.978 --> 36:32.106
Let it play out. They don't have anything,
they're bluffing.

36:32.190 --> 36:34.960
You don't know that, Alex. You told me
you don't know that. You don't...

36:34.984 --> 36:37.104
But if you were in trouble,
they would've come to you.

36:38.070 --> 36:39.197
They have no idea.

36:40.865 --> 36:43.326
Clay will get off.
You can walk, it'll be fine.

36:43.409 --> 36:44.409
Alex, I killed...

36:45.494 --> 36:46.704
